text: Robert Taylor is an Australian professional rugby union football coach. He is currently the head coach of the Sydney University Football Club and was the Head Coach of the 2019 NSW Country Eagles team that plays in the NRC competition. Robert had previously had numerous coaching roles in . Taylor will be joining Leicester Tigers from the 2020/21 season onwards as an Assistant Coach. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Australian rugby union coaches Category:1980 births Category:Leicester Tigers coaches
